---
title: Double Chicken & Creamy Chive Sauce with Wedges & Greens
description: With their delicate onion flavour and vibrant colour, chives make a sauce sing! This creamy chive sauce for seared chicken
breast is packed with flavour, and with roasted potatoes and garlicky veggies on the side, it makes a meal everyone will love.
